comment: Favors (UTA) and Iguodala (GSW) make incidental contact with one another while going after the loose ball.
Burks (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Curry's (GSW) breakaway layup attempt. Any contact on the play is initiated by Curry.
Hood (UTA) makes contact with Green's (GSW) arm that affects his layup attempt.
Curry (GSW) and Burks (UTA) briefly engage and separate during the inbounds play.
Favors (UTA) sets the screen on Thompson (GSW) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Green (GSW) is late to the spot and makes contact with Favors' (UTA) body that affects his shot attempt.
Ezeli (GSW) jumps vertically and legally contests Hood's (UTA) driving layup attempt.
After Gobert (UTA) sets a legal screen on Iguodala (GSW), the two players briefly engage and separate.
Burks (UTA) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Curry (GSW) legally contests Hayward's (UTA) half-court shot attempt.
